title: H3 After Dark (Defending Trisha From The Wicked David Portnoy) - #17
description: On this FINAL episode of 2020 the gang take some time to look back on another year of goofs gaffs and splaffs, take a call from our old bud ShoeNice who has some explaning to do- AB and Love have a SIMP off, and Ian hosts the first annual Craigsmas! Thanks for listening everyone and see you all in 2021!!!
